race.comment: INQUISITOR (8) ran well below his best last time over 1600m at Doomben, beaten 4 lengths into eighth at $4.20. This easier and deserves another chance. STRIKE THE HEART (14) has been in the market at her last couple of runs but failed to threaten, the latest effort a modest fifth at Sunshine Coast over 1400m. Rates highly in this line up and gets her chance. BLINDING SPEED (10) finished fifth two runs back at Sunshine Coast then improved last time out to score by a nose after being in contention on the turn over 1540m at Gold Coast Poly. Looks well placed so expect another big run. I STOLE IT (6) closed off strongly last start to get up for second, beaten a head, over 1400m at Gold Coast. Should be winding up late again.
